<i># Reople on the street now</i>

01:17:18.000 --> 01:17:19.991
<i># Faces long and grim</i>

01:17:21.503 --> 01:17:23.562
<i># Souls are feeling heavy and</i>

01:17:23.639 --> 01:17:24.731
<i>(dog barks)</i>

01:17:24.806 --> 01:17:27.502
<i># Faith is growing thin</i>

01:17:28.610 --> 01:17:30.407
<i># Fears are getting stronger</i>

01:17:30.479 --> 01:17:33.141
<i># You can feel them on the rise</i>

01:17:34.216 --> 01:17:37.049
<i># Hopelessness got some by the throat</i>

01:17:37.119 --> 01:17:40.418
<i># You can see it in their eyes</i>

01:17:40.489 --> 01:17:43.424
