01:17:47.029 --> 01:17:49.827
<i># I said, "How come?"</i>

01:17:53.301 --> 01:17:54.393
<i>(rings doorbell)</i>

01:17:54.503 --> 01:17:56.596
<i># How come?</i>

01:17:59.374 --> 01:18:01.569
Hi. I'm looking for my wife.

01:18:08.250 --> 01:18:11.083
- Whose Ferrari is that?
- My stepfather's here.

01:18:22.497 --> 01:18:24.192
Hey, nice car.

01:18:24.266 --> 01:18:25.927
- <i>(dog barks)</i>
- Rachel...

01:18:28.103 --> 01:18:32.403
Just how badly do you hate me
to have to live with this lie?

01:18:32.474 --> 01:18:34.408
I don't hate you.

01:18:37.112 --> 01:18:40.138
- You're on private property.
- Hi, Georgia. I'm...

01:18:40.882 --> 01:18:42.782
Just give me a moment, OK?

01:18:46.621 --> 01:18:49.089
I shouldn't have agreed to pass you off

01:18:49.157 --> 01:18:52.320
to someone who you don't know
because I didn't have the patience.

01:18:52.394 --> 01:18:56.922
I should've taken the time.
I should've been there.

01:18:56.998 --> 01:18:59.023
What are you doing here?

01:19:02.170 --> 01:19:04.331
- What am I doing here?
- Yeah.

01:19:04.406 --> 01:19:08.934
You called me to tell me you're leaving me,
and then you hang up?

01:19:09.010 --> 01:19:11.740
And you wanna know what I'm doing here?

01:19:13.181 --> 01:19:18.084
If I had touched my daughter,
I wouldn't be here, would I?

01:19:19.955 --> 01:19:22.947
Come on, honey. Please. You...

01:19:24.693 --> 01:19:27.457
You know me better than anyone on earth.

01:19:27.529 --> 01:19:31.260
- She told me...
- What did she tell you? Huh?

01:19:31.333 --> 01:19:35.793
That she wasn't using drugs
when you found LSD in her room? Huh?

01:19:35.871 --> 01:19:40.899
That she wasn't stealing from you
when I found your emerald ring in a pawn shop?

01:19:40.976 --> 01:19:44.935
Or that she hadn't been drinking
when she crashed her car?

01:19:46.081 --> 01:19:48.140
How many lies have I told?

01:19:48.216 --> 01:19:51.117
Oh, please. You're a lawyer.

01:19:51.853 --> 01:19:54.981
I am fighting for my life, goddammit.

01:19:55.056 --> 01:19:57.547
Don't speak to her like that.

01:20:04.633 --> 01:20:05.429
OK.

01:20:07.402 --> 01:20:13.830
If this was something I couldn't change -
an accident, an illness - I'd accept it.

01:20:13.909 --> 01:20:17.003
She would not lie
about something like this.

01:20:18.213 --> 01:20:20.272
Would I?

01:20:22.217 --> 01:20:24.014
I don't know.

01:20:24.085 --> 01:20:26.815
Honey, please. Please.

01:20:29.491 --> 01:20:32.324
Put this in your mouth,
get in your car, and drive.

01:20:32.394 --> 01:20:36.455
I love your daughter, and I love Rachel,
and I would never do anything...

01:20:36.531 --> 01:20:39.796
- What are you doing?
- You do not take the Lord's name in vain.

01:20:39.868 --> 01:20:42.701
You do not fool around
with little girls. Drive.

01:20:42.771 --> 01:20:45.069
I'm not moving.
I am staying right here.

01:20:47.576 --> 01:20:51.569
- Swear to God, I never touched her.
- Save it for the appeal.

01:20:51.646 --> 01:20:56.310
If you don't put that in your mouth soon,
I'm gonna dismantle your car.

01:20:56.384 --> 01:20:58.352
OK.

01:20:59.821 --> 01:21:02.119
I'm leaving. All right?

01:21:05.427 --> 01:21:10.831
I'll be here until Lilly's ready
to come home to San Francisco, OK?

01:21:28.817 --> 01:21:30.785
What if he's innocent?

01:21:30.852 --> 01:21:34.015
Well, it felt really good anyway.

01:21:42.197 --> 01:21:42.891
Rachel...

01:21:44.566 --> 01:21:45.328
Rachel...

01:21:46.868 --> 01:21:50.133
- Can I talk to you?
- No.

01:21:50.205 --> 01:21:52.435
Can you talk to me?

01:21:55.777 --> 01:21:56.505
Rachel.

01:22:01.049 --> 01:22:06.180
I'm at the only motel in this town,
next to the Halfway House Café.

01:22:06.688 --> 01:22:09.521
Lil, just hear me out, please.

01:22:10.558 --> 01:22:15.621
Rachel will get over her anger and take back this lie
one day, but where will you and I be?

01:22:15.697 --> 01:22:20.225
What kind of life will we have led
until that happens?

01:22:20.302 --> 01:22:23.169
I just don't want you to regret not believing me.

01:22:23.238 --> 01:22:27.766
But I need you here with me, now.

01:22:33.515 --> 01:22:35.449
I don't know who to believe.

01:22:37.118 --> 01:22:41.282
You have to believe that
I wanted her to go to rehab, but, uh...

01:22:41.356 --> 01:22:47.625
you said no, remember? You said
you didn't wanna get into your own demons, right?

01:22:49.898 --> 01:22:52.526
That's true.

01:22:54.803 --> 01:22:57.670
- Can I get you anything?
- No, thank you.

01:22:57.739 --> 01:22:59.866
Nothing? No baked potato special...

01:22:59.941 --> 01:23:02.171
- You're just gonna sit there?
- It's fine.

01:23:02.243 --> 01:23:05.041
I'll take care of you. Thank you.

01:23:08.149 --> 01:23:12.984
I'll do anything
to show you how much I love you

01:23:13.054 --> 01:23:16.820
and how easy it is for me
to forgive her. OK?

01:23:18.626 --> 01:23:22.687
We'll find our way through this.
I know we can.

01:23:22.764 --> 01:23:24.459
Rachel. Oh...

01:23:26.101 --> 01:23:28.899
I didn't know where you were.
Are you OK?

01:23:30.305 --> 01:23:32.773
I'm fine, Grandma.

01:23:34.509 --> 01:23:39.708
I want you to stay there at Simon's.
And I think probably your mom's gonna call.

01:23:39.781 --> 01:23:43.376
- OK?
- Yeah. OK, I'll talk to you later.

01:23:44.185 --> 01:23:47.586
I have to go. I'm cooking Simon dinner.

01:23:47.655 --> 01:23:49.646
I love you, sweetie.

01:23:51.393 --> 01:23:53.293
<i># Can you count on me?</i>

01:23:53.361 --> 01:23:55.022
<i># I won't let you down...</i>

01:23:55.096 --> 01:23:56.028
<i>(knock on door)</i>

01:23:56.097 --> 01:23:58.691
<i># ...woman is so sensational</i>

01:23:58.767 --> 01:24:01.099
<i># No, you can count on</i> me...

01:24:01.302 --> 01:24:02.997
- Hello?
- <i>(knocking)</i>

01:24:03.938 --> 01:24:06.406
- Who is it?
- Me.

01:24:11.379 --> 01:24:13.438
Hi.

01:24:13.515 --> 01:24:16.848
- I need a bathroom.
- OK. Are you OK?

01:24:18.386 --> 01:24:21.355
This way. Make a left.
Right here on the left.

01:24:21.423 --> 01:24:23.414
<i>(coughs/throws up)</i>

01:24:25.827 --> 01:24:27.658
I'll get you water.

01:24:36.471 --> 01:24:37.460
<i>(music stops)</i>

01:24:38.540 --> 01:24:40.701
Here you go.

01:24:40.775 --> 01:24:42.402
I...

01:24:43.178 --> 01:24:47.877
It's always so much easier to believe what you need
than what you know.

01:24:47.949 --> 01:24:49.940
I need Arnold.

01:24:51.186 --> 01:24:55.680
He has me convinced.
And you have me convinced.

01:24:58.626 --> 01:25:01.288
He finally got his Ferrari, huh?

01:25:07.969 --> 01:25:10.301
Help me understand.

01:25:11.406 --> 01:25:17.936
I need to just tell you what I feel,
because all I saw was how much you loved him.

01:25:18.012 --> 01:25:20.480
How much he loved you.

01:25:21.950 --> 01:25:24.316
How much he loves me.

01:25:27.455 --> 01:25:30.515
And I thought, "How lucky we are."

01:25:31.392 --> 01:25:38.457
I just can't fit what he's done
with who I always thought he was.

01:25:41.569 --> 01:25:43.799
I came to tell you I believe you.

01:25:46.274 --> 01:25:48.208
I like your hair short.

01:25:48.276 --> 01:25:52.007
And that none of this is your fault.

01:25:53.381 --> 01:25:55.906
None of this is your fault.

01:26:04.392 --> 01:26:06.986
I really did just say it to make a point.

01:26:10.698 --> 01:26:12.529
What?

01:26:14.702 --> 01:26:18.297
Simon believed me.
Grandma believed me.

01:26:20.375 --> 01:26:23.276
Mom, I just wanted to see if you did.

01:26:32.921 --> 01:26:35.014
Oh, please...

01:26:37.559 --> 01:26:39.823
I screwed up with Vassar.

01:26:39.894 --> 01:26:44.263
I screwed it all up, and I knew
I wasn't ever coming home again.

01:26:44.732 --> 01:26:47.929
And I wanted both of you
to pay for my mistakes.

01:26:50.171 --> 01:26:54.972
You can be mad at me if you want.
And tell him I'm sorry.

01:26:57.178 --> 01:27:00.045
He's not even angry with you.

01:27:00.114 --> 01:27:02.412
He's ready to forgive you.

01:27:11.726 --> 01:27:14.320
I might need a little time.

01:28:19.694 --> 01:28:21.662
<i># I can wait, I can wait</i>

01:28:21.729 --> 01:28:24.960
<i># I can sit wondering what in the world</i>

01:28:25.033 --> 01:28:27.558
<i># You think about</i>

