01:28:37.045 --> 01:28:40.139
<i># And drunken shouts</i>

01:28:40.214 --> 01:28:43.547
<i># I don't think I'm ever gonna figure it out</i>

01:28:44.886 --> 01:28:48.788
<i># Like some wild last frontier</i>

