<i># I don't think I'm ever gonna figure it out</i>

01:29:13.848 --> 01:29:15.941
It was good. Thank you.

01:29:16.017 --> 01:29:17.917
You're welcome.

01:29:17.985 --> 01:29:23.423
When my mom was too drunk to cook, I used to
take whatever was in the fridge and put it in a pot.

01:29:28.062 --> 01:29:29.962
What's going on?

01:29:31.399 --> 01:29:33.390
Same old thing.

01:29:36.104 --> 01:29:39.301
Your mom called.
She wants to say good night.

01:29:41.275 --> 01:29:43.869
I'm here, home, at Grandma's.

01:29:44.545 --> 01:29:47.412
- Would you come over?
- No.

01:29:48.015 --> 01:29:49.448
OK.

01:29:50.818 --> 01:29:52.308
Well, good night, then.

01:29:52.387 --> 01:29:55.049
Please come back to San Francisco.

01:29:56.157 --> 01:29:58.284
No, Mom, not right now.

01:29:58.960 --> 01:30:02.896
We can't leave it like this.
We have to talk.

01:30:02.964 --> 01:30:06.024
Can you call me in the morning?

01:30:06.768 --> 01:30:08.998
Yeah, OK.

01:30:10.671 --> 01:30:11.729
OK.

01:30:11.806 --> 01:30:13.831
OK.

